title: PostgreSQL: Connections
agents: linux
catalog: app/postgresql
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check allows you to monitor the amount of active and idle connections to a database.
 You can configure limits for the absolute connection count or percentual
 limits in respect to the maximum allowed active and idle connections.
 This check relies on data reported by the agent-side plugin {mk_postgres}

item:
 Name of the category and the name of the database

discovery:
 One service is created for each database.
